<p>
    The collected data is used solely to:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Manage household tasks</li>
    <li>Organize family schedules</li>
    <li>Provide a clear overview of family responsibilities</li>
</ul>

<h3>Data Security</h3>
<p>
    FamilyFlow does not share data with third parties. All information is used only within the application.
